info.author: OpenStack
classifiers: License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License
info.name: sushy-tools
info.summary: A set of tools to support the development and test of the Sushy library (http://sushy.readthedocs.io/)

vulnerabilities.details: An issue was discovered in OpenStack Sushy-Tools through 0.21.0 and VirtualBMC through 2.2.2. Changing the boot device configuration with these packages removes password protection from the managed libvirt XML domain. NOTE: this only affects an "unsupported, production-like configuration."
